ores of 65.7/52.0 on\nLaSOT/TNL2K, which are on par with recent state of the arts. Code and models\nwill be released.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2022 16:22:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-10"}
