mation parameter constraints. Our results show that\nthe global 21-cm signal is a promising test-bed for WDM models, even in the\npresence of strong degeneracies with astrophysical parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2022 19:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 19:04:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
